sorcer.util

Class ProviderLocator

  • java.lang.Object
    • sorcer.util.ProviderLocator

  • public class ProviderLocator
extends java.lang.Object
    ProviderLoactor is a simple wrapper class over Jini's LookupDiscovery. It which returns the first matching instance of a service either via unicast or multicast discovery with support for SORCER signatures
